###EKS node polices to add
AmazonEKSWorkerNodePolicy
AmazonEKS_CNI_Policy
AmazonEC2ContainerRegistryReadOnly

EKS Using CloudFormation
install awscli
install eksctl #installation instructions on aws websit ###  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/eks/latest/userguide/eksctl.html
install kubectl #installation instructions on aws websit ###  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/eks/latest/userguide/install-kubectl.html
aws --version
eksctl version
kubectl version
#configure awscli by running
aws configure  [add your key and secret]
eksctl create help for commands help
eksctl create cluster --name sirgeks --region us-east-1 --zones us-east-1a, us-east-1c --nodegroup-name worker-nodes --node-type t2-micro --managed
 
 ##delete cluster
 eksctl delete cluster --name ntech-eks-cli --region us-east-2
